quran[11{c,v,t}:
7,12,"poocha,"" tujhe kis cheez ne sajda karne se roka jab ke mein ne tujh ko hukum diya tha ?"" bola,"" mein uss se behtar hon, to ne mujhe aag se peda kya hai aur ussay matti se """
7,13,"farmaya,"" acha to yahan se neechay utar tujhe haq nahi hai ke yahan barayi ka ghamand kere nikal ja ke Dur haqeeqat to un logon mein se hai jo khud apni zillat chahtay hain """
7,14,"bola,"" mujhe uss din taq mohlat day jab ke yeh sab dobarah uthaye jayen ge """
7,15,"farmaya,"" tujhe mohlat hai """
7,16,"bola,"" acha to jis terhan to ne mujhe gumraahi mein mubtala kya mein bhi ab teri seedhi raah par"
7,17,"inn insanon ki ghaat mein laga rahon ga, agay aur peechay, dayen aur baen, har taraf se inn ko ghayron ga aur to un mein se aksar ko shukar guzaar nah paye ga """
7,18,"farmaya,"" nikal ja yahan se zaleel aur thukraya howa yaqeen rakh ke inn mein se jo teri pairwi karen ge, tujh sameit un sab se jahannum ko bhar dun ga"
7,19,"aur ae aadam, to aur teri biwi, dono is jannat mein raho, jahan jis cheez ko tumhara jee chahay khao, magar is darakht ke paas nah phatakna warna zaalmon mein se ho jao ge """
7,20,"phir shetan ne unn ko behkaya taakay un kisharmghain jo aik dosray se chhupayi gayi theen un ke samnay khol day is ne un se kaha,"" tumahray rab ne tumhe jo is darakht se roka hai is ki wajah iss ke siwa kuch nahi hai ke kahin tum farishtay nah ban jao, ya tumhe hameshgi ki zindagi haasil nah ho jaye"
7,21,aur is ne qasam kha kar un se kaha ke mein tumhara sacha kher khuwa hon
7,22,"is terhan dho ka day kar woh un dono ko rafta rafta apne dhab parlay aaya aakhir kaar jab unhon ne is darakht ka maza chakkha to un ke sattar aik dosray ke samnay khil gay aur apne jismon ko jannat ke pattoun se dhanknelagey tab un ke rab ne inhen puraka,"" kya mein ne tumhe is darakht se nah roka tha aur nah kaha tha ke shetan tumhara khula dushman hai? """
